snippet.title: Diner Bros Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/846800/Diner_Bros/
Website: http://www.dinerbros.com

Join the Diner Bros as they frantically cook, serve, and upgrade their restaurant in 1-4 player couch co-op action.  Don't leave your customers hungry and waiting!
